          "en-US": "Senior Launcher"
        },
        "summary": {
          "en-US": "Android launcher for seniors"
        },
        "description": {
          "en-US": "Senior Launcher is an Android launcher app designed for older users, with a simplified interface, visual accessibility, and optional remote control through a backend.\n\n<b>What it is</b>\n\n- Main Android launcher with simple navigation.\n- Includes built-in mini apps: phone, SMS, camera, gallery, and flashlight.\n- Lets you choose and sort allowed apps shown on the home screen.\n- Can optionally sync with a backend for real-time remote control.\n"
        },
